Class Patient

java.lang.Object
com.group6.hms.app.managers.auth.User
com.group6.hms.app.roles.Patient
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Patient extends User
The Patient class represents a patient in the hospital management system. It extends the User class and contains attributes and methods specific to a patient such as contact information, phone number, and medical record.
